@Daniell Mesquita: First the plugin resolves `yourdomain.zeroid` using the ZeroID certificate database. If the address contains any subdomains, the plugin waits for `yourdomain.zeroid/content.json` to be downloaded and reads `domain_records` table from there. For example:

```
 "domain_records": {
  "talk.zeronet.ru.0h.zeroid": "1TALK5znjVqrULiRUiSuNALaCiKpWS1Xq",
  "zeronet.ru.0h.zeroid": "1zeroRvxd42DSWUETotiaa8k5a5mDGvJs",
  "zerowiki.0h.zeroid": "138R53t3ZW7KDfSfxVpWUsMXgwUnsDNXLP"
 },
```

